title: Teen shot and killed in the 100 block of East Tenny Ave.
content:
LOUISVILLE, Ky. (WHAS11) – Louisville Metro Police responded to a report of shots fired in the 100 block of East Tenny Ave.
When police arrived at the scene, they found a male, Asian juvenile shot.
The victim was transferred to University Hospital where he was later pronounced dead.
The LMPD Homicide Unit is investigating the case.
Police said there are no suspects at this time.
If anyone has any information is asked to call the anonymous tipline at 574-LMPD.
